## Architecture Before vs. After

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Current (v1.3.0)"
        A1[ALW_Shipping_Calculator] -->|"hooks into"| B1[woocommerce_package_rates]
        B1 -->|"replaces ALL rates"| C1[Checkout]
    end

    subgraph "After (v1.4.0)"
        A2[ALW_Distance_Service] -->|"provides distance"| B2[ALW_Shipping_Method]
        B2 -->|"extends"| C2[WC_Shipping_Method]
        C2 -->|"registered in"| D2[Shipping Zones]
        D2 -->|"adds rate alongside others"| E2[Checkout]
    end
```
